bilingual.source: She set her work aside to focus on her family.
bilingual.target: 她把工作放在旁边，专注于家庭。

bilingual.source: We set the argument aside and continued working.
bilingual.target: 我们把争论放在旁边，继续工作。

bilingual.source: He put his worries aside and enjoyed the vacation.
bilingual.target: 他把烦恼放在旁边，享受假期。

bilingual.source: You stand aside. Your hand on my shoulder.
bilingual.target: 鉨站在旁边, 手放在皒肩上.

bilingual.source: He was doing his homework, his dog sitting aside.
bilingual.target: 他正在做家庭作业，狗坐在旁边（陪着）。

bilingual.source: They sat aside 100 channels, each 200 kilohertz wide.
bilingual.target: 他们在旁边坐了100种渠道, 各200千赫宽.

bilingual.source: A storage room is set aside especially to deposit fresh bamboo-which is the staple food for the pandas in their natural habitat.
bilingual.target: 尤其是在旁边建了一个存储室用来存放竹子——对于熊猫来说，竹子是它们与生俱来的主食。

bilingual.source: He stepped aside to let her pass.

yingyinNormal.en: Throw a joke or aside in. It will draw laugh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 讲个笑话，聊点闲话，逗逗观众。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《公开场合演讲如何展现自信？》

yingyinNormal.en: You must set aside your petty grievances with the dwarves.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们对矮人的小牢骚可以放在一边了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies》

yingyinNormal.en: Thank goodness, you're here. Stand aside. Doctor Hamster's here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你能来太高兴了。请大家让一让，仓鼠兽医来了。

yingyinNormal.en: All assurances aside, what really concerns me is accountability. Accountability?
yingyinNormal.zh: 先不谈这些保证，我担心的是责任。责任？

yingyinNormal.en: All right, I won't set one aside for you. But I must have it. Okay, I'll set one aside for you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，那我不给你留了。但我必须要拥有它行。那我给你留着。

yingyinNormal.en: Wait a minute, all jokes aside? I didn't agree to that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等等，撇开笑话不提？我可不同意。

yingyinNormal.en: Set all but two tablespoons of oil aside for the sauce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 留两汤匙油做酱汁用。

yingyinNormal.en: We don't want her gone, we just want to nudge her aside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不是想她走人，只是让她靠边站。

yingyinNormal.en: Is there anyone here aside from my friend Yusuf who cannot…
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里的人除了我朋友玉素甫外还有谁是不能…

yingyinNormal.en: If the governors desire my removal, I will, of course, step aside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果理事们都希望我离职，那么我当然应该走了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: What are you talking about? Don't toss the mission aside, Francis.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你说什么呢？别放弃维和任务，弗兰西斯。

yingyinNormal.en: The other governors and I have decided it's time for you to step aside.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还有其他的理事都认为该是你走的时候了。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Spock, in this case do yourself a favor. Put aside logic. Do what feels right.
yingyinNormal.zh: 史波克，别为难你自己了，把理智放一边，做你想做的事吧。

yingyinNormal.en: We must put aside all talks of death, and focus on birth. The birth of a new age.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们不要谈论死亡，而要关注诞生。新时代的诞生。

yingyinNormal.en: Ross let me ask you a question. All jokes aside, where is this relationship going?
yingyinNormal.zh: 罗斯，我问你撇开笑话不提，这段感情要往哪里走？

yingyinNormal.en: What were you doing at the opera tonight? What? Aside from killing the Chancellor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你今晚在歌剧院干什么？除了暗杀总理还有别的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This is why you put a brawler like Barney Hull in office, aside from paying a debt.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这就是你让巴尼·豪尔这样的强人当选的原因，不只是还他人情。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, Ross, if anyone should step aside, it should be Ben. What? Chandler, tell him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 罗斯，如果真有人要退出，那也应该是班。什么？ 钱德，告诉他为什么。

yingyinNormal.en: You can't do this. I own 10% of the company. Your father set those shares aside for me.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不能这么做，我有公司10%的股份，是你父亲留给我的公司股份。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《爱丽丝梦游仙境2：镜中奇遇记》

yingyinNormal.en: But let's put that aside for a moment and talk about your good friend. Who? Senator Austen.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先不谈那个，来说说你的好朋友。谁？奥斯汀参议员。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: If the bills become law, state boards and commissions will be required to set <highlight>aside</highlight> 50 percent of board seats for women by 2022.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果该提案成为法律，各州的董事会和委员会将被要求在2022年之前为女性留出50%的董事会席位。

examination_example.sentence: The fund will also be used to compensate landowners who set <highlight>aside</highlight> habitat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该基金还将用于补偿那些放弃栖息地的土地所有者。

examination_example.sentence: The financial impatience is like "children who pick the plums out of their pudding to eat at once" rather than putting them <highlight>aside</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 财务上的不耐烦就像“从布丁里挑出李子马上吃的孩子”而不是把它们放在一边。

examination_example.sentence: Nostalgia for ink on paper and the rustle of pages <highlight>aside</highlight>, there's plenty of incentive to ditch print.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 抛开对纸上油墨和书页沙沙声的怀念，放弃印刷的动机很充足。
